CREATE TABLE "Answer" (
	"AnswerText" VARCHAR(10000) NULL,
	"SurveyID" INTEGER NULL,
	"UserID" INTEGER NULL,
	"QuestionID" INTEGER NULL
)

CREATE TABLE "Question" (
	"questiontext" VARCHAR(1000) NULL,
	"questionid" INTEGER NULL
)

CREATE TABLE "Survey" (
	"SurveyID" INTEGER NOT NULL,
	"Description" VARCHAR(255) NULL,
	PRIMARY KEY ("SurveyID")
)
